see the change in her, and they were proud of her. And while it wasn't easy, Sophie had realized that the key to gaining independence was to never give up, to keep pushing forward, and to take risks.\n\nSophie knew that life would never be the same again, but she was okay with that. She had discovered who she was and what she was capable of, and that was a victory in itself."}
